              </div>
              <div class="opp-desc">Sofia turned 17 last month and holds a learner's permit per public records. Adding her now establishes a driving record with your carrier.</div>
              <div class="opp-meta">
                <span>Est. premium: +$680/yr</span>
                <span>3 min flow</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="opp-card">
              <div class="opp-row">
